title: Jessica Korda Takes 2-Shot Lead in LPGA Malaysia
text:
Published By: NYTimes Golf - Today 
Jessica Korda took a two-stroke lead Saturday in the LPGA Malaysia, shooting a bogey-free 6-under 65 in sweltering conditions....
